Package org.openpnp.spi

Interface TransformedAxis

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Axis, Identifiable, Named, PropertySheetHolder, Solutions.Subject, WizardConfigurable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSingleTransformedAxis, AbstractTransformedAxis, ReferenceCamClockwiseAxis, ReferenceCamCounterClockwiseAxis, ReferenceLinearTransformAxis, ReferenceMappedAxis
    public interface TransformedAxis
extends Axis
    A TransformedAxis is a Cartesian or rotary dimension on the machine that is transformed from/to a ControllerAxis. There are simple single axis transforms and multi-axis transforms that need to be solved over all the axes.
